{"tid":1178520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍士兵縫「令機員再次強大」及特朗普肖像臂章 軍服涉違政治中立","createTime":"2019-05-30T12:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T15:29:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5081f5e18e5a7a1a7bd9116bfb3078a97d041ca0","tid":1178520,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190529/photo/bkn-20190529180049471-0529_00972_001_01p.jpg?20190529180347\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190529%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190529180049471-0529_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20190529180347&h=7bd7c9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普周二（28日）離開日本前，登上美軍兩棲攻擊艦黃蜂號慰問士兵。不過，有士兵的軍服被拍到縫上「令機員再次強大」（Make Aircrew Great Again）的臂章 ，明顯改自特朗普的競選口號。海軍調查這有否違反國防部有關政治中立的規定。<br />\n<br />\n由傳媒拍到的照片可見，至少一名海軍陸戰隊隊員的軍服上，縫有該個引起爭議的臂章。它不但縫有改自特朗普競選口號「令美國再次強大」的字句，更附有特朗普的肖像。不過，根據軍方的軍服標準及規則，士兵穿上軍服時不得進行黨派政治的行為。<br />\n<br />\n對此，海軍發表簡短聲明回應，指軍方領導層正檢視此事，以確保士兵軍服的臂章不會違反任何政策或規則。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190529/photo/bkn-20190529180049471-0529_00972_001_02b.jpg?20190529180347\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190529%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190529180049471-0529_00972_001_02b.jpg%3F20190529180347&h=cf2d3576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普向士兵發表講話。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190529/photo/bkn-20190529180049471-0529_00972_001_03b.jpg?20190529180347\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190529%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190529180049471-0529_00972_001_03b.jpg%3F20190529180347&h=4e085051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普（右）登上黃蜂號視察。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190529/bkn-20190529180049471-0529_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190529%2Fbkn-20190529180049471-0529_00972_001.html&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1aCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=c6abdddc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190529/bkn-20190529180049471-0529_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/05/29/politics/navy-review-trump-patches/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F05%2F29%2Fpolitics%2Fnavy-review-trump-patches%2Findex.html&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1aCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=fac6a64f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F05%2F29%2Fpolitics%2Fnavy-review-trump-patches%2Findex.html&h=7857e605\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/05/29/politics/navy-review-trump-patches/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b9a8f3d06c94e7e352724a900fce8c2498ebc64","tid":1178520,"uid":121146,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:49:15.000Z","msg":"講事實都唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deca65776aad51e262b73dfcab645f828dd14daf","tid":1178520,"uid":46943,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:51:16.000Z","msg":"係香港你唔歸邊先唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61220c98f8737765a2e24b87ab25997e37672eb3","tid":1178520,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:53:45.000Z","msg":"trump's private crew<br />\nnot america <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a93f6e03e2d2494a8cb5f0044c88501ef55210","tid":1178520,"uid":114275,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"美軍炒佢 升佢做侵仔近身侍衛"},{"pid":"63e863de82a01ecd1c57fe2b44a15cedfc534689","tid":1178520,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b31c64bd7abdfc285926ad56af93666fb3f8ac","